style.css:
@-moz-document domain("www.whitescreen.online") {
/*  Dark Mode for whitescreen.online  */
/*  by ShaneX                         */
/*  X.com/ShaneX                      */
/*  -- For questions, bugs, help,     */
/*     well wishes, boredom, etc.     */
  
/*
  UserStyles.org may just be the worst website experience 
  I have experienced in 20 years of online activities.
  9 times out of 10 simple edits to the CSS code throw errors
  when there are no errors in the code. Then the 10th time, w/o
  rewriting any code, the "Save & Publish" button FINALLY works.
  I hope they find some way to get a skilled engineer on board
  that is willing to help at least make the site usable. As it
  sits it is such a waste of years of quality work.
  
  NOTE: If this style does not appear to work in browsers other than Firefox, it is because of the way the site forced the code to have a moz-document header. Chrome and Vivaldi users can just remove the first 2 lines, as well as the opening curly bracket on the 3rd line, and the closing curly bracket on the last line of css code. This was primarily developed and used on Google Chrome/Vivaldi so it should prove to work best in those browsers. Feel free to contact me in comments here or @ShaneX on X.com (Twitter) with any questions or bugs.
*/

html {
    background-color: #000000;
    color: #696969;
}

body {
    background-color: #000000;
    color: #696969;
}

h1, h2 {
    color: #696969;
}

.site-name a {
    color: #f0f0f0;
}

.feedback {
    color: #222222;
}

.lang-dropbtn {
    background-color: #000000;
    color: #222222;
}

.main-color {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px 0 #3366ff;
}

button {
    color: #424242;
    background-color: #000000;
    border: 1px solid #424242;
    -webkit-border-radius: 3px;
    -moz-border-radius: 3px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin: 0px 5px 0px 5px;
}

.download-btn {
    margin-top: 15px;
}

#open-on-all-screens {
    margin-bottom: 25px;
}

select, input, label {
    color: #222222;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #222222 !important;
}

.gallery a, .gallery-right-color, .color-right-text {
    color: #424242;
}

@media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .gallery-left {
        padding-top: 0px;
        padding-bottom: 0px;
        padding-right: 10px;
        width: 174px;
    }
    .color-block {
        padding: 0px 0px 5px 0px;
    }
}

.color-block-selected {
    background-color: #1e2035;
  }
}
